title: Oct. 09, 2015 OECS Leaders to attend Solidarity Summit in Dominica (Government of Grenada)
text: ( Source : Government of Grenada ) ST. GEORGE 'S, GRENADA, OCTOBER 9, 2015 , GOVERNMENT INFORMATION SERVICE ( GIS ): Dominica will host the next summit of the leaders of the OECS next month. This was disclosed on Friday during a solidarity visit
